{
  "$schema": "../../schemas/mcp-registry.schema.json",
  "name": "github",
  "version": "1.0.0",
  "title": "GitHub",
  "description": "Interact with GitHub repositories, issues, pull requests, and more",
  "category": "development",
  "source": "official",
  "tags": ["github", "git", "repositories", "issues", "pull-requests"],
  "icon": "/registry-logos/github.svg",
  "icon_background": {
    "light": "#efeae7",
    "dark": "#6a6a89"
  },
  "color": "#24292F",
  "about": "## GitHub MCP\n\nInteract with GitHub to manage repositories, issues, pull requests, and more directly from your AI assistant.\n\n### Features\n\n- **Repository Management** - Create, fork, and manage repositories\n- **Issues & PRs** - Create, update, and search issues and pull requests\n- **Code Search** - Search code across repositories\n- **File Operations** - Read and create/update files\n\n### Authentication\n\nRequires a GitHub Personal Access Token (PAT) with appropriate scopes.\n\n### Required Scopes\n\n- `repo` - Full control of private repositories\n- `read:user` - Read user profile data\n\n### Manual Configuration\n\nIf you prefer to configure this MCP server manually in your client without using the Scooter 'Install' button, use the settings below:\n\n#### Claude Desktop / Cursor\n\nAdd this to your `claude_desktop_config.json` or `mcp.json`:\n\n```json\n{\n  \"mcpServers\": {\n    \"github\": {\n      \"command\": \"npx\",\n      \"args\": [\"-y\", \"@modelcontextprotocol/server-github\"],\n      \"env\": {\n        \"GITHUB_TOKEN\": \"YOUR_PERSONAL_ACCESS_TOKEN_HERE\"\n      }\n    }\n  }\n}\n```\n\n#### Zed\n\nAdd this to your `settings.json`:\n\n```json\n{\n  \"mcp_servers\": {\n    \"github\": {\n      \"command\": \"npx\",\n      \"args\": [\"-y\", \"@modelcontextprotocol/server-github\"],\n      \"env\": {\n        \"GITHUB_TOKEN\": \"YOUR_PERSONAL_ACCESS_TOKEN_HERE\"\n      }\n    }\n  }\n}\n```\n\n#### Gemini CLI\n\nAdd this to your `settings.json`:\n\n```toml\n[mcp.servers.github]\ncommand = \"npx\"\nargs = [\"-y\", \"@modelcontextprotocol/server-github\"]\n[mcp.servers.github.env]\nGITHUB_TOKEN = \"YOUR_PERSONAL_ACCESS_TOKEN_HERE\"\n```",
  "homepage": "https://github.com",
  "repository": "https://github.com/anthropics/mcp-github",
  "documentation": "https://docs.github.com/en/rest",
  "authorization": {
    "type": "bearer_token",
    "required": true,
    "env_var": "GITHUB_TOKEN",
    "display_name": "GitHub Personal Access Token",
    "description": "A GitHub PAT with repo and read:user scopes",
    "help_url": "https://github.com/settings/tokens/new",
    "scopes": ["repo", "read:user"]
  },
  "tools": [
    {
      "name": "search_repositories",
      "title": "Search Repositories",
      "description": "Search for GitHub repositories by name, description, or other criteria.",
      "inputSchema": {
        "type": "object",
        "properties": {
          "query": {
            "type": "string",
            "description": "Search query (supports GitHub search syntax)"
          },
          "page": {
            "type": "integer",
            "description": "Page number for pagination",
            "default": 1
          },
          "per_page": {
            "type": "integer",
            "description": "Results per page (max 100)",
            "default": 30
          }
        },
        "required": ["query"]
      },
      "sampleInput": {
        "query": "language:typescript stars:>1000",
        "per_page": 10
      },
      "annotations": {
        "readOnlyHint": true,
        "openWorldHint": true
      }
    },
    {
      "name": "get_file_contents",
      "title": "Get File Contents",
      "description": "Retrieve the contents of a file from a GitHub repository.",
      "inputSchema": {
        "type": "object",
        "properties": {
          "owner": {
            "type": "string",
            "description": "Repository owner (username or organization)"
          },
          "repo": {
            "type": "string",
            "description": "Repository name"
          },
          "path": {
            "type": "string",
            "description": "Path to the file in the repository"
          },
          "branch": {
            "type": "string",
            "description": "Branch name (defaults to default branch)"
          }
        },
        "required": ["owner", "repo", "path"]
      },
      "sampleInput": {
        "owner": "facebook",
        "repo": "react",
        "path": "README.md"
      },
      "annotations": {
        "readOnlyHint": true
      }
    },
    {
      "name": "create_issue",
      "title": "Create Issue",
      "description": "Create a new issue in a GitHub repository.",
      "inputSchema": {
        "type": "object",
        "properties": {
          "owner": {
            "type": "string",
            "description": "Repository owner"
          },
          "repo": {
            "type": "string",
            "description": "Repository name"
          },
          "title": {
            "type": "string",
            "description": "Issue title"
          },
          "body": {
            "type": "string",
            "description": "Issue body (markdown supported)"
          },
          "labels": {
            "type": "array",
            "items": { "type": "string" },
            "description": "Labels to apply to the issue"
          }
        },
        "required": ["owner", "repo", "title"]
      },
      "sampleInput": {
        "owner": "your-username",
        "repo": "your-repo",
        "title": "Bug: Example issue title",
        "body": "## Description\n\nDescribe the issue here.",
        "labels": ["bug"]
      },
      "annotations": {
        "readOnlyHint": false,
        "destructiveHint": false
      }
    },
    {
      "name": "create_pull_request",
      "title": "Create Pull Request",
      "description": "Create a new pull request in a GitHub repository.",
      "inputSchema": {
        "type": "object",
        "properties": {
          "owner": {
            "type": "string",
            "description": "Repository owner"
          },
          "repo": {
            "type": "string",
            "description": "Repository name"
          },
          "title": {
            "type": "string",
            "description": "Pull request title"
          },
          "body": {
            "type": "string",
            "description": "Pull request description"
          },
          "head": {
            "type": "string",
            "description": "The branch containing your changes"
          },
          "base": {
            "type": "string",
            "description": "The branch you want to merge into"
          }
        },
        "required": ["owner", "repo", "title", "head", "base"]
      },
      "sampleInput": {
        "owner": "your-username",
        "repo": "your-repo",
        "title": "feat: Add new feature",
        "body": "## Summary\n\nThis PR adds...",
        "head": "feature-branch",
        "base": "main"
      },
      "annotations": {
        "readOnlyHint": false,
        "destructiveHint": false,
        "requiresApproval": true
      }
    },
    {
      "name": "push_files",
      "title": "Push Files",
      "description": "Create or update files in a GitHub repository.",
      "inputSchema": {
        "type": "object",
        "properties": {
          "owner": {
            "type": "string",
            "description": "Repository owner"
          },
          "repo": {
            "type": "string",
            "description": "Repository name"
          },
          "branch": {
            "type": "string",
            "description": "Branch to push to"
          },
          "files": {
            "type": "array",
            "items": {
              "type": "object",
              "properties": {
                "path": { "type": "string" },
                "content": { "type": "string" }
              }
            },
            "description": "Files to create or update"
          },
          "message": {
            "type": "string",
            "description": "Commit message"
          }
        },
        "required": ["owner", "repo", "branch", "files", "message"]
      },
      "sampleInput": {
        "owner": "your-username",
        "repo": "your-repo",
        "branch": "main",
        "files": [
          { "path": "example.txt", "content": "Hello, World!" }
        ],
        "message": "Add example file"
      },
      "annotations": {
        "readOnlyHint": false,
        "destructiveHint": true,
        "requiresApproval": true
      }
    }
  ],
  "package": {
    "type": "npm",
    "name": "@modelcontextprotocol/server-github",
    "version": "^1.0.0"
  },
  "runtime": {
    "transport": "stdio",
    "command": "npx",
    "args": ["-y", "@modelcontextprotocol/server-github"]
  },
  "metadata": {
    "author": "Anthropic",
    "license": "MIT"
  }
}
